## Quick visualization

Before running any model it's important to take a look at the data. We can, for instance, 
visualize the block effect on the trait. 



::: {.cell}

```{.r .cell-code}
data |>
  ggplot(aes(x = gen, y = yield, color = block)) +
  geom_point(size = 3) +
  theme_classic(base_size = 15)
```

