We can now show the estimation and their variances alltogether 



::: {.cell}

```{.r .cell-code}
data.frame(
  coefficient = rownames(vcov_betas),
  solution = beta,
  variance = diag(vcov_betas),
  std.error = sqrt(diag(vcov_betas)),
  row.names = NULL
) |> gt()
```

